#How to apply for voter ID Card?
Voter ID is a citizen card approved by the Government of India. Which proves that you are a citizen of India. You must be 18 years old to receive it. To download your voter list you need to login to the Election Commission website and fill out the form and provide your personal information. Your voter list will be included after verification by the Election Commissioner.


#How to download voter id list?
To download the voter list you must have the 2020 voter list or the 2020 voter list your name. If your name is not included in the list then you have to apply again as you will be able to download the EPIC number section voter ID, which is included in the going voter list.
